Name: Description
Overcrowded Rental Housing: Occupied rental housing units with more than one person per room.

Name: Source Notes
Overcrowded Rental Housing: U.S. Census Bureau, American Community Survey 1-Year Estimates, Table B25014 (2005-2019, 2021-2022); retrieved from https://data.census.gov/.

Name: Notes
Overcrowded Rental Housing: Please note, we do not report 2020 American Community Survey 1-year estimates. Due to disruptions and biases in data collection during 2020, the Census Bureau released the “experimental” 1-year estimates for 2020 and advises against comparing against estimates from prior or future years.
